@{
    ViewBag.Title = "PGDM Program - ASBM";
}
<h2 class="page-title">🎓 Post Graduate Diploma in Management (PGDM)</h2>
<p class="sub-title">Transforming Aspirants into Business Leaders</p>

<div class="pgdm-container">
    <div class="pgdm-box">
        <h3>📖 Comprehensive Curriculum</h3>
        <p>Our PGDM program is designed to equip students with cutting-edge knowledge in core business disciplines such as Finance, Marketing, Human Resources, and Business Analytics.</p>
        <p>Learn through case studies, real-world simulations, and project-based assessments to develop analytical and decision-making skills.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pgdm-box">
        <h3>🏛️ Specializations for Future Leaders</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>📊 Business Analytics</li>
            <li>💰 Finance</li>
            <li>📈 Marketing</li>
            <li>👥 Human Resource Management</li>
            <li>🌍 International Business</li>
            <li>🔍 Operations & Supply Chain Management</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Tailor your learning experience with specialized courses and workshops aligned with industry demands.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pgdm-box">
        <h3>🌍 Industry Exposure & Corporate Connect</h3>
        <p>🔹 Gain hands-on industry experience through internships with top MNCs.</p>
        <p>🔹 Participate in live projects, business conclaves, and corporate mentorship programs.</p>
        <p>🔹 Network with business leaders through guest lectures, industry visits, and alumni interactions.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pgdm-box">
        <h3>📚 Expert Faculty & Innovative Pedagogy</h3>
        <p>Learn from distinguished academicians and experienced corporate professionals.</p>
        <p>Our faculty members use interactive teaching methodologies, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>🎭 Case-Based Learning</li>
            <li>📺 Business Simulations</li>
            <li>🎤 Leadership Development Programs</li>
            <li>💡 Problem-Solving Workshops</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="pgdm-box">
        <h3>🎯 100% Placement Assistance & Career Opportunities</h3>
        <p>We ensure career success through our dedicated placement cell, which connects students with recruiters from top companies like:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>🏦 Banking & Finance: HDFC, ICICI, Axis Bank</li>
            <li>🛍️ Retail & E-commerce: Amazon, Flipkart, Reliance</li>
            <li>🏢 Consulting & Analytics: Deloitte, KPMG, PwC</li>
            <li>🎯 Marketing & FMCG: Unilever, Nestlé, Coca-Cola</li>
        </ul>
        <p>🔥 Resume-building workshops, mock interviews, and soft skills training enhance employability.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pgdm-box">
        <h3>📅 Program Duration & Eligibility</h3>
        <p>⏳ Duration: 2 Years (Full-Time) | AICTE Approved</p>
        <p>✅ Eligibility: Graduate (Minimum 50%) + Entrance Exam (CAT/MAT/XAT/CMAT)</p>
        <p>📍 Location: Aditya School of Business Management, Mumbai</p>
    </div>
</div>

